I got an idea.

23
00:00:54,294 --> 00:00:55,895
I know things haven't been easy for you.

24
00:00:56,095 --> 00:00:56,755
They're gonna get better.

25
00:00:56,995 --> 00:00:57,596
You promise?

26
00:00:58,916 --> 00:00:59,736
I pinky promise.

27
00:00:59,897 --> 00:01:01,477
That's the most solemn vow there is.

28
00:01:01,877 --> 00:01:02,638
Where do we start?

29
