Pretty sure I've gained about 150 pounds in the last two weeks.

43
00:01:35,668 --> 00:01:37,668
You could change her life, Mr. Wonka.

44
00:01:38,289 --> 00:01:40,049
Change all their lives.

45
00:01:41,469 --> 00:01:42,890
Run away!

46
00:01:43,750 --> 00:01:46,831
Every good thing in this world started with a dream.

47
00:01:49,552 --> 00:01:50,832
So you hold on to yours.

48
00:01:55,497 --> 00:02:01,378
Mark my words, this is going to be the greatest chocolate shop the world has ever seen.

49
