Allow me to refresh your memory.

53
00:02:16,401 --> 00:02:17,581
Oh, I don't think I want to hear that.

54
00:02:17,701 --> 00:02:18,041
Too late.

55
00:02:18,701 --> 00:02:19,622
I've started dancing now.

56
